data.description: This fabulous Home features 2 bed rooms and 1.5 bath rooms, physically the property has 4 bedrooms but  records show only 2/1.5, very spacious bed rooms, laminated wood floor through the whole house, very open floor plan Living/ dining area connecting to the Kitchen with ceramic tile floors and well maintained cabinets, a den is to the left on the entry area, inside laundry hook-ups, very spacious back yard, Close to USC, Exposition Park, Downtown LA, shops, restaurants, transportation and more!
